comments: McGee (LAL) slightly extends his arm into McCollum (POR), but the contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
McGee (LAL) extends two hands to Harkless' (POR) midsection during his driving shot attempt.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) moves laterally into Harkless' (POR) path to initiate contact in transition. Harkless goes to, not through, Caldwell-Pope's body.
Kanter (POR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Kanter (POR) makes contact to Caruso's (LAL) head which affects his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Williams (LAL) and he does not deliver contact.
Caruso (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Caldwell-Pope's (LAL) arm and does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Kanter (POR) has a marginal resting hand that he slightly follows-through with to Muscala's (LAL) body, but doesn't affect his ability to defend Harkless' (POR) shot attempt.
Curry (POR) reaches in and cleanly steals the ball from Caruso (LAL).
Williams (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
